ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisReappointment of ROSA B. WALKER of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years; and designation of ROSA B. WALKER as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board.
